column8: So now we gave 5 particles making up the universe: protons, neutrons, electrons, photons and morons. The latter particles form governments.
Or maybe they got it wrong.

Once you hear particle physicists say "hypothetical" you are in the area of philosophy and not empiricism. If you've ever talked to a particle physicist about their work, it is quite clear they are out of the realm of science.
You may be right. He may be right,  she may be right, and I may be right.
So let me get this straight, hypothetical matter is made of hypothetical protons?Is this really science?
First nuclear fusion, now this! Is AI already at work,and where are we going????
Ладно. Наука всё дальше и дальше забирается в неизведанное для простого смертного!
Kind of like how Dark Souls went to Epstein's Island....
Гагарин като се приземиш чакам те в къщи!
"Темные фотоны" могут быть тем, что составляет темную материю - исследование
